Forecast.io (JSON)
	- Accuracy: ~2Â°

	Ranges:
	- Current conditions
	- Minute-by-minute forecasts out to 1 hour (where available)
	- Hour-by-hour forecasts out to 48 hours
	- Day-by-day forecasts out to 7 days

	Data:
	- ALERTS
	- Time
	- Summary
	- Icon
	- Precipitation (intensity, probability, type)
	- feels like
	- Cloud Cover
	- Wind (direction, intensity) 
